            <div class="editable">
        <div class="featurePanelInner">
    
        <h3>About the journal</h3>
        
    
    <p><em>Social History of Medicine</em>, the journal of the <a data-link-id="4f59fe4a-663e-4a12-bbb7-bc1a4ecf3f5c" href="https://sshm.org/"><em>Society for the Social History of Medicine</em></a>, is concerned with all aspects of health, illness, and medical treatment in the past. It is committed to publishing work on the social history of medicine from a variety of disciplines …</p>

    
    
    <a href="https://sshm.org/">Find out more</a>
       
</div>

            </div>
    </div>
    
    
